data.title: Call of Duty®: Warzone Season 05
data.meta_description: In the new Call of Duty®: Warzone Season 05, experience new gameplay features, modes, and a new event. Discover new weapons like the MRAP light tactical vehicle, get in the driver’s seat in the new Armored Royale mode, and embark on the Champion’s Quest on Vondel  in this new season of the popular battle royale game.
data.text:
DROP IN, ARMOR UP, LOOT FOR REWARDS, AND BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP.

Welcome to Warzone, the massive free-to-play combat arena from the world of Modern Warfare®.

Drop In

Join forces with your friernds and jump into a battleground with up to 150 players.

Loot For Rewards

Discover supply boxes and complete contracts to build your arsenal and gain a tactical advantage.

Battle Across Two Epic Modes

Experience a new way to 'Battle Royale' or play 'Plunder' in a race to earn the most Cash in the match.
